welcome_message_body: "Welcome to Tleta Taghramt, Morocco! Prepare to be enchanted by the city's vibrant culture, rich history, and stunning landscapes. We invite you to immerse yourself in the charm of this city and explore all it has to offer. Enjoy your stay and make unforgettable memories."
